   Cao, Yuan; Su, Feiming; Wu, Xianguo, Huazhong Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Civil \& Hydraul Engn, Wuhan 430074, Hubei, Peoples R China.
   Antwi-Afari, Maxwell Fordjour, Aston Univ, Coll Engn \& Phys Sci, Dept Civil Engn, Birmingham B4 7ET, England.
