Affiliation = {Erden, C (Corresponding Author), Sakarya Univ Appl Sci, Fac Appl Sci, Sakarya, Turkiye.
   Kurnaz, Talas Fikret, Mersin Univ, Tech Sci Vocat Sch, Transportat Serv, Mersin, Turkiye.
