   esti-mation; Support Vector Machine (SVM); Wireless Sensor Network (WSN)},
Keywords-Plus = {OF-CHARGE ESTIMATION; LITHIUM-ION BATTERY; EXTENDED KALMAN FILTER;
   NEURAL-NETWORKS; STATE; MODEL; HEALTH},
Author-Email = {khairiishak@usm.my},
Number-of-Cited-References = {72},
