Affiliation = {Xin, Q (Corresponding Author), Univ Faroe Isl, Fac Sci \& Technol, DK-100 Torshavn, Faroe Islands, Denmark.
   Jain, Deepak Kumar; Li, Yongfu, Chongqing Univ Posts \& Telecommun, Key Lab Intelligent Air Ground Cooperat Control U, Coll Automat, Chongqing 400065, Peoples R China.
