   Bekiros, Stelios; Bezzina, Frank, Univ Malta, FEMA, MSD-2080 Msida, Malta.
   Bekiros, Stelios, London Sch Econ \& Polit Sci LSE, LSE Hlth, London WC2A2AE, England.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.eswa.2022.118349},
EarlyAccessDate = {AUG 2022},
