   Borgli, Rune Johan; Stensland, Hakon Kvale; Riegler, Michael Alexander; Halvorsen, Pal, Univ Oslo, Oslo, Norway.
   Riegler, Michael Alexander; Halvorsen, Pal, Simula Metropolitan Ctr Digital Engn, Oslo, Norway.},
DOI = {10.1109/ismict.2019.8743779},
Keywords = {hyperparameter optimization; bayesian optimization; keras; medical
