   Baili, Jamel, King Khalid Univ, Coll Comp Sci, Dept Comp Sci, Abha 61413, Saudi Arabia.
   Khan, Muhammad Attique, Prince Mohammad Bin Fahd Univ, Coll Comp Engn \& Sci, Dept Artificial Intelligence, POB 1664, Al Khobar 31952, Saudi Arabia.
   Hamza, Ameer, HITEC Univ, Dept Comp Sci, Taxila 47080, Pakistan.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jneumeth.2024.110247},
EarlyAccessDate = {AUG 2024},
