Affiliation = {Gungor, VC (Corresponding Author), Abdullah Gul Univ, Dept Comp Engn, Kayseri, Turkey.
   Gormez, Yasin; Aydin, Zafer; Gungor, Vehbi C., Abdullah Gul Univ, Dept Comp Engn, Kayseri, Turkey.
