   Elshaboury, Nehal, Housing \& Bldg Natl Res Ctr, Construct \& Project Management Res Inst, Giza, Egypt.
   Ibrahim, Ahmed Hussien, Zagazig Univ, Dept Construct \& Util, Zagazig, Egypt.
   Elyamany, Ahmed Hussien, British Univ, Civil Engn Dept, El Shorouk, Egypt.},
