   Mashhadzadeh, Amir Hamed; Kostas, Konstantinos V., Nazarbayev Univ, Sch Engn \& Digital Sci, Dept Mech \& Aerosp Engn, 53 Kabanbay Batyr Ave, Astana 010000, Kazakhstan.
   Kadyr, Aidyn, Nazarbayev Univ, Sch Sci \& Humanities, Dept Math, Astana 010000, Kazakhstan.
   Spitas, Christos, Univ Nottingham, Sch Aerosp Engn, Ningbo, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.commatsci.2024.112998},
