   Shandilya, Abhishek; Sundararaman, Ravishankar, Rensselaer Polytech Inst, Mat Sci \& Engn, Troy, NY 12180 USA.
   Schadler, Linda S., Univ Vermont, Coll Engn \& Math Sci, Burlington, VT 05405 USA.},
DOI = {10.3390/nano13172394},
