   Huang, Ze-Ning; Zhang, Hao-Xiang; Sun, Yu-Qin; Zhang, Xing-Qi; Weng, Cai-Ming; Zheng, Chao-Hui; Wang, Jia-Bin; Chen, Qi-Yue; Cao, Long-Long; Lin, Mi; Tu, Ru-Hong; Huang, Chang-Ming; Lin, Jian-Xian; Xie, Jian-Wei, Fujian Med Univ, Key Lab, Minist Educ Gastrointestinal Canc, Fuzhou, Peoples R China.
