   Holena, M (Corresponding Author), Leibniz Inst Katalyse eV, Albert Einstein Str 29a, D-18059 Rostock, Germany.
   Korel, Lukas, Czech Tech Univ, Fac Informat Technol, Prague 16636, Czech Republic.
   Yorsh, Uladzislau, Charles Univ Prague, Fac Math \& Phys, Prague 16636, Czech Republic.
   Behr, Alexander S.; Kockmann, Norbert, TU Dortmund Univ, Fac Biochem \& Chem Engn, D-44227 Dortmund, Germany.
   Holena, Martin, Czech Acad Sci, Inst Comp Sci, Prague 16636, Czech Republic.
   Holena, Martin, Leibniz Inst Katalyse eV, Albert Einstein Str 29a, D-18059 Rostock, Germany.},
DOI = {10.3390/computers12010014},
